%h1 Servers

%p
  The following communities are running CloudThreads servers.

- @servers.each do |server|
  .server.media
    .server-price.float-xs-right
      %h4 $20/mo

    .media-left
      .server-logo.float-xs-left.align-middle{ style: "background-image: url(#{server.logo_url});" }
    .media-body.server-body
      %h4
        = server.name
      .server-description.text-muted
        = server.description
      .server-stats
        %span.tag.tag-default.server-stat
          Users
          %strong= server.user_count
        %span.tag.tag-default.server-stat
          Local Boards
          %strong= server.local_board_count
        %span.tag.tag-default.server-stat
          Local Threads
          %strong= server.local_thread_count
        %span.tag.tag-default.server-stat
          Local Messages
          %strong= server.local_message_count
